App-ZofCMS-Plugin-YouTube

The module is a plugin for L<App::ZofCMS>. It provides means to have a
CRUD-like (Create, Read, Update, Delete) interface for managing YouTube
videos. The plugin provides a form where a user can enter the title of
the video, its YouTube URI and a description. That form is stored
in a SQL database by the plugin and can be displayed as a list.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc App::ZofCMS::Plugin::YouTube

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=App-ZofCMS-Plugin-YouTube

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/App-ZofCMS-Plugin-YouTube

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/App-ZofCMS-Plugin-YouTube

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/App-ZofCMS-Plugin-YouTube


